%^CYAN%^Psions%^RESET%^ are able to select a discipline that represents their inner nature.

%^BOLD%^%^WHITE%^Be aware%^RESET%^ - you cannot change discipline without <abandon>ing some levels in your class, so choose wisely..

%^CYAN%^Discipline specific spells are as follows:%^RESET%^

%^CYAN%^Egoist:%^RESET%^
    animal affinity
    chameleon
    lesser transformation
    thicken skin
%^CYAN%^Seer:%^RESET%^ 
    aura sight
    clairvoyance
    hypercognition
    prying eyes
    sending
    speak with dead
%^CYAN%^Shaper:%^RESET%^ 
    astral construct
    call crystals
    hail of crystals
    planar portal
    psionic teleport
%^CYAN%^Kineticist:%^RESET%^ 
    control object
    energy cone
    energy current
    reddopsi
    tornado blast
%^CYAN%^Nomad:%^RESET%^
    call crystals
    planar portal
    planar sending    
    psionic teleport
%^CYAN%^Telepath:%^RESET%^ 
    domination
    mindnet
    modify memory
    sending
    speak with dead
   

%^CYAN%^See also:%^RESET%^ psion, discipline roleplay


